== 制作 ==
=== 演员选择 ===
{{quote box|width=25em|align=right|quote=“一开始的时候，这些人都是各过各的，到了电影的高潮桥段，大家都走上舞台。所以这实际讲述的是个起初各奔东西的家庭最后团结在一起的故事。”|source=——编剧[[迈克尔·阿恩特|迈克尔·阿恩特]]<ref name="ForaInterview">{{cite web | url = http://fora.tv/2007/02/15/Little_Miss_Sunshine_Shooting_Script | title = Little Miss Sunshine: The Shooting Script | publisher = [http://fora.tv/ FORA.tv] | date = 2007-02-15 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140701133701/http://fora.tv/2007/02/15/Little_Miss_Sunshine_Shooting_Script | archivedate = 2014-07-01 }}</ref>}}
导演乔纳森·戴顿和维莱莉·法瑞斯请来拍摄音乐视频期间合作过的选角导演金·戴维斯（{{lang|en|Kim Davis}}）和贾斯汀·巴德利（{{lang|en|Justine Baddely}}）协助本片的选角工作<ref name="TwitchFilm">{{cite news | title = Little Miss Sunshine—Interview With Valerie Faris and Jonathan Dayton | last = Gullién | first = Michael | publisher = Twitch | date = 2006-07-20 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | url = http://twitchfilm.com/2006/07/little-miss-sunshineinterview-with-valerie-faris-and-jonathan-dayton.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131110004125/http://twitchfilm.com/2006/07/little-miss-sunshineinterview-with-valerie-faris-and-jonathan-dayton.html | archivedate = 2013-11-10 }}</ref>。他们先是选定由格雷戈·金尼尔饰演理查德·胡佛<ref name="EpochTimesInterview">{{cite news | title = Directors of New Surprise Hit 'Little Miss Sunshine' Under the Spotlight | last = Balfour | first = Bradley | work = The Epoch Times | date = 2007-02-20 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | url = http://www.theepochtimes.com/news/7-2-20/51902.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120819174919/http://www.theepochtimes.com/news/7-2-20/51902.html | archivedate = 2012-08-19 }}</ref>。对于谢丽尔·胡佛一角则是在考虑了多位[[女演员|女演员]]后再决定由[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]的托妮·克莱特扮演<ref name="EpochTimesInterview" />。据报道称，戴维斯和巴德利走遍了“每一个英语国家”<ref name="TwitchFilm" />来寻找合适的小演员出演奥莉弗·胡佛，最终入选的阿比盖尔·布蕾斯琳参加试镜时还只有6岁。保罗·达诺得到德韦恩一角时距电影开拍还有两年，为了做好演出准备，他还花了几天时间像片中角色一样立誓不再说话<ref name="EpochTimesInterview" /><ref name="MovieWebProd">{{cite news | title = About the Production | author = Fox Searchlight Pictures | publisher = el racó interactiu de cinema | accessdate = 2012-02-16 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www2.terrassa.cat/educacio/raco_interactiu_cinema/Activitats2007/04_little_miss_sunshine.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120216111627/http://www2.terrassa.cat/educacio/raco_interactiu_cinema/Activitats2007/04_little_miss_sunshine.pdf | archivedate = 2012-02-16}}</ref>。导演们起初觉得艾伦·阿金对于诠释埃德温·胡佛一角来说太过年轻，但他最终还是得到了这个角色<ref name="EpochTimesInterview" />。

片中曾试图[[自杀|自杀]]的学者弗兰克一角起初是为[[比尔·莫瑞|比尔·莫瑞]]设计，制片公司还曾要求请[[罗宾·威廉斯|罗宾·威廉斯]]出演<ref name="NYTSmallFilm">{{cite news |title=A Small Film Nearly Left for Dead Has Its Day in the Sundance Rays |last=Waxman |first=Sharon |work=The New York Times |date=2006-01-23 |deadurl=no |publisher=The New York Times Company |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/01/23/movies/MoviesFeatures/23sund.html?_r=0 |accessdate=2014-07-22 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vWbd0KPQ?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/01/23/movies/MoviesFeatures/23sund.html?_r=2 |archivedate=2011-01-06 }}</ref>，但两位导演一直到影片开拍几个月前才选择了史蒂夫·卡瑞尔，对此他们在接受采访时称：“考虑到史蒂夫·卡瑞尔之前的工作经验，我们并没有在一开始就把他设想成这个角色的人选。但当我们见面并且对人物进行探讨后，（我们发现）无论是在电影的基调还是希望达成的效果方面，他都与我们有所共识”<ref name="TwitchFilm" /><ref name="EpochTimesInterview" />。卡瑞尔之前曾连续多年参加获得观众高度评价的讽刺新闻节目《[[每日秀|乔恩·斯图尔特每日秀]]》演出，是[[喜剧中心|喜剧中心]]频道观众熟悉的演员，但在获选出演《阳光小美女》时，他在[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]相对来说还是默默无闻<ref name="MovieWebProd" />。电影的几位制片人还曾担心卡瑞尔缺乏足够的演出经验，并且名气上也不够响亮<ref name="EWSunshineBand">{{cite news|title=The Sunshine Band |last=Rottenberg |first=Josh |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2006-08-03 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1222576,00.html |accessdate=2014-07-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104012200/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C1222576%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-11-04 }}</ref>。

=== 剧本和发展 ===
本片的剧本由[[迈克尔·阿恩特|迈克尔·阿恩特]]编写，起初的公路旅程设置在[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]，从[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]出发到达[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]，但由于预算上的问题而改成了新墨西哥州到加利福尼亚州<ref name="AOLTravel">{{cite news | last = Moore | first = Roger | title = Directors keep their 'Sunshine' out of the Sunshine State | work = Orlando Sentinel | url = http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/2006-08-18/entertainment/SUNSHINEGUYS_1_dayton-abigail-breslin-sunshine | date = 2006-08-16 | accessdate = 2013-12-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131204020910/http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/2006-08-18/entertainment/SUNSHINEGUYS_1_dayton-abigail-breslin-sunshine | archivedate = 2013-12-04}}</ref>。阿恩特于2000年5月23日动笔，同月26日就完成了初稿<ref name="ScriptBook">{{cite book | last = Arndt | first = Michael | title = Little Miss Sunshine: The Shooting Script | url = https://archive.org/details/littlemisssunshi00arnd | date = 2007-02-06 | isbn = 1-55704-770-7 | page = x | publisher = Newmarket Press | location = New York}}</ref>。他起初还打算亲自筹集数千美元用台[[摄影机|摄影机]]拍完这部电影<ref name="DVDCommShoot">{{cite video | title = Little Miss Sunshine-(Commentary by Jonathan Dayton, Valerie Faris, and Michael Arndt) | medium = DVD | publisher = 20th Century Fox | time = 11:33 | date = 2006-12-19}}</ref>，但之后还是把剧本交给了制片人罗恩·耶克萨和阿尔伯特·伯格，两位[[制片人|制片人]]组建了深河制片厂，开始寻找潜在[[导演|导演]]人选<ref name="FindItsWay">{{cite journal | last = Ortner | first = Sherry B. | title = Little Miss Sunshine Finds Its Way | journal = Anthropology News | volume = 48 | issue = 2007-10 | pages = 22–23 | date = 2007-10-10 | url = http://www.anthrosource.net/Abstract.aspx?issn=1541-6151&volume=48&issue=7&doubleissueno=0&article=245257&suppno=0&jstor=False | format = Registration required | doi = 10.1525/an.2007.48.7.22 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archive-date = 2013-12-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203004916/http://www.anthrosource.net/Abstract.aspx?issn=1541-6151&volume=48&issue=7&doubleissueno=0&article=245257&suppno=0&jstor=False | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

制片人在制作《[[呢个校园选乜鬼|校园风云]]》期间认识了导演戴顿和法瑞斯，并在2001年把本片的剧本拿给了他们。两人之后表示：“这部电影真是引起了我们的共鸣，感觉就像为我们量身定做的一般”<ref name="NYTSmallFilm" />。这是阿恩特编写的第一部剧本，制片人马克·图特尔陶布于2001年12月21日以25万美元的价格买下<ref name="ScriptBook2">{{cite book | last = Press | first = Skip | title = The Complete Idiot's Guide to Screenwriting | publisher = Penguin Group | edition = 3rd | year = 2008 | isbn = 1-59257-755-5 | page = 252 | location = New York}}</ref>。耶克萨和伯格继续留任制片人，负责物色导演和摄影师、协助最后的重拍以及帮助把影片带到[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]参展<ref name="EpochTimesInterview" /><ref name="LATimesProducers">{{cite news|title=The unkindest cut |last=Goldstein |first=Patrick |work=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2007-02-22 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.calendarlive.com/movies/cl-et-gold20feb20,0,7118982.story?coll=cl-movies |date=2007-02-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070222213129/http://www.calendarlive.com/movies/cl-et-gold20feb20%2C0%2C7118982.story?coll=cl-movies |archivedate=2007-02-22 }}</ref>。

几位主创联系了多家制片公司，只有[[焦点影业|焦点影业]]表示有兴趣，该公司还希望电影在[[加拿大|加拿大]]拍摄<ref name="NYTSmallFilm" />。制片公司希望影片更专注于理查德·胡佛一角，但阿恩特不同意，于是他遭到解雇<ref name="ForaInterview" />。接替的编剧增加了多段剧情，例如理查德与一位贬损自己工作能力的角色之间的对抗<ref name="DVDCommWriter">{{cite video | title = Little Miss Sunshine-(Commentary by Jonathan Dayton, Valerie Faris, and Michael Arndt) | medium = DVD | publisher = 20th Century Fox | time = 46:30 | date = 2006-12-19}}</ref>。但这位新编剧在对剧本进行了4周的改写后退出了项目，并且这时制片公司也出现企业变革，有新的负责人上任，阿恩特又重新获聘回到了项目中<ref name="SF360">{{cite news | title = Michael Arndt, Little Mr. Sunshine | last = Guillén | first = Michael | publisher = SF360 | date = 2007-02-23 | url = http://www.sf360.org/features/2007/02/michael_arndt_l.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071221183235/http://www.sf360.org/features/2007/02/michael_arndt_l.html | archivedate = 2007-12-21 | accessdate = 2007-12-21 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。经过两年的前期制作，焦点影业于2004年8月放弃了本片的制作。马克·图特尔陶布付给焦点影业40万美元买回影片版权并对该公司的开发成本提供一定的补偿<ref name="NYTSmallFilm" />。他还支付了《阳光小美女》拍摄花费的800万美元预算<ref name="USAShadows">{{cite news | title='Sunshine,' out of the shadows | last = Bowles | first = Scott | work = USA Today | date = 2006-08-28 | deadurl = no | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/music/news/2006-08-27-sunshine-hit_x.htm | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023171541/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/music/news/2006-08-27-sunshine-hit_x.htm | archivedate = 2012-10-23}}</ref>。

=== 拍摄 ===
电影的主体拍摄工作于2005年6月6日展开<ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/2005/film/news/trio-going-on-road-trip-1117921010/ | title = Trio going on road trip | last = Fleming | first = Michael | work = Variety | date = 2005-04-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140722071716/http://variety.com/2005/film/news/trio-going-on-road-trip-1117921010/ | archivedate = 2014-07-22}}</ref>，分别在[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]和[[南加州|南加州]]取景，一共花了30天时间，拍摄顺序与剧本中的情节次序一致<ref name="TwitchFilm" /><ref name="MovieWebProd" /><ref name="LATimesProducers" />。阿恩特于影片在圣丹斯电影节上映仅6星期前改写了结局，这部分镜头在2005年12月拍摄<ref name="DVDCommEnding">{{cite video | title = Little Miss Sunshine-(Commentary by Jonathan Dayton, Valerie Faris, and Michael Arndt) | medium = DVD | publisher = 20th Century Fox | time = 1:35:41 | date = 2006-12-19}}</ref>。后期制作完成仅4天后，本片就在电影节的9张银幕上放映，电影的[[首演|首映式]]也在这里举行<ref name="EpochTimesInterview" /><ref name="NewsBlaze">{{cite news | title = "Little Miss Sunshine", Sundance Festival Film, Shows Its Glorious Colors | last = Bandler | first = Michael | publisher = [http://newsblaze.com/ ''NewsBlaze''] | date = 2006-01-29 | url = http://newsblaze.com/story/20060129093017nnnn.nb/topstory.html | accessdate = 2013-02-06 | deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130206125116/http://newsblaze.com/story/20060129093017nnnn.nb/topstory.html | archivedate = 2013-02-06}}</ref>。制片人皮特·萨拉夫的侄女丽贝卡·安尼托（{{lang|en|Rebecca Annitto}}）于2005年9月14日因车祸遇难，因此片尾的字幕表示本片是献给她的作品，并且花絮镜头中还出现了餐馆和便利店<ref name="Dedicate">{{cite news | title = Family sues in death of girl who inspired 'Little Miss Sunshine' | agency = Associated Press | work = Home News Tribune | date = 2007-04-03 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/mycentraljersey/doc/437949117.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Apr%2003,%202007&author=&pub=Home%20News%20Tribune&edition=&startpage=&desc=Family%20sues%20in%20death%20of%20girl%20who%20inspired%20'Little%20Miss%20Sunshine' | format = Fee required | archive-date = 2015-01-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150112133250/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/mycentraljersey/doc/437949117.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Apr%2003,%202007&author=&pub=Home%20News%20Tribune&edition=&startpage=&desc=Family%20sues%20in%20death%20of%20girl%20who%20inspired%20'Little%20Miss%20Sunshine' | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==== 大众{{lang|en|T2}}面包车 ====
[[File:LittleMissSunshineCast.jpg|thumb]]
阿恩特在编写剧本的过程中根据自己的经验和车辆的实用性选择采用大众T2面包车作为片中的主要交通工具，对此他表示：“我还记得自己当时在想，找辆什么样的车来进行这段公路旅行呢？大众看起来符合逻辑，车子比较高，视线开阔，你有较为充足的空间可以放置摄影机。从前面的挡风玻璃往后就能看到每一个人”<ref name="ForaInterview" />。剧组一共使用了5辆大众面包车来进行拍摄，车辆还做了些改进，以便适应不同的拍摄需要<ref name="DVDCommVan5">{{cite video | title = Little Miss Sunshine-(Commentary by Jonathan Dayton, Valerie Faris, and Michael Arndt) | medium = DVD | publisher = 20th Century Fox | time = 23:10 | date = 2006-12-19}}</ref>。只有三辆车上有[[发动机|发动机]]，另外两辆则是装在拖车上<ref name="DVDCommVan5" />。前期制作期间，摄影师使用基本镜头在车内调整方向，以便找到最理想的拍摄角度<ref name="MovieWebProd" />。阿恩特小时候的一次旅行使用的也是同一型号的车，一路上出现了许多类似片中车辆的问题，例如[[离合器|离合器]]损坏、喇叭不停地响以及关不紧的门<ref name="SF360" /><ref name="DVDCommVanProblems">{{cite video | title = Little Miss Sunshine-(Commentary by Jonathan Dayton, Valerie Faris, and Michael Arndt) | medium = DVD | publisher = 20th Century Fox | time = 31:22 | date = 2006-12-19}}</ref><ref name="DVDCommVanProblems2">{{cite video | title = Little Miss Sunshine-(Commentary by Jonathan Dayton, Valerie Faris, and Michael Arndt) | medium = DVD | publisher = 20th Century Fox | time = 1:01:51 | date = 2006-12-19}}</ref>。

拍摄片中一家人推车的镜头时，剧组为保证演员们的安全而请来一位特技协调员<ref name="EpochTimesInterview" />。对此男演员格雷戈·金尼尔在接受采访时有些开玩笑地表示：“我大概是以80公里时速开着这辆没有侧面安全气囊的71年大众面包车。基本上你要等着这辆巨型镜头卡车从我们眼前带着摄像头呼啸而过。‘好了，出发！’我想这真是疯了，这是我拍过的最危险的电影”<ref name="MovieWebint">{{cite news | title = Interview: Riding In The Little Yellow Van With Little Miss Sunshine | last = Chupnick | first = Steven | publisher = [http://www.movieweb.com/ Movie Web] | date = 2006-07-26 | url = http://www.movieweb.com/news/riding-in-the-little-yellow-van-with-little-miss-sunshine | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120728133843/http://www.movieweb.com/news/riding-in-the-little-yellow-van-with-little-miss-sunshine | archivedate = 2012-07-28 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。拍摄车中镜头期间，众演员一天经常要在车里待上三到四个小时<ref name="MovieWebint" />。摄制艾伦·阿金的角色满嘴脏话的镜头时，布蕾斯琳就像片中自己扮演的人物一样带上了耳机，这样她就听不到老人的对白。一直到看到最终完成的电影时她才知道当时阿金到底说了些什么<ref name="MovieWebint" /><ref name="CinCon">{{cite news | title = Interview: Alan Arkin and Abigail Breslin in "Little Miss Sunshine" | last = Aames | first = Ethan | publisher = [http://www.cinecon.com/ Cinema Confidental] | date = 2006-07-19 | url = http://www.cinecon.com/news.php?id=0607193 | accessdate = 2011-10-27 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111027011005/http://www.cinecon.com/news.php?id=0607193 | archivedate = 2011-10-27}}</ref>。2006年7月25日，[[福克斯探照灯影业|福克斯探照灯影业]]邀请大众面包车主到加利福尼亚州[[工业市_(加利福尼亚州)|工业市]]观看本片，有超过60辆车到达了放映现场<ref name="FoxBuses">{{cite web | url = http://www2.foxsearchlight.com/littlemisssunshine/slideshow/ | title = Little Miss Sunshine VW Drive in City of Industry, CA on July 25th | publisher = Fox Searchlight Pictures | accessdate = 2012-04-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120420052743/http://www2.foxsearchlight.com/littlemisssunshine/slideshow/ | archivedate = 2012-04-20}}</ref>。

==== 选美比赛 ====
[[File:LittleMissSunshinePageant.jpg|thumb]]的角色（中）看起来体型比其他女孩大，她穿上了填充式的服装。片中选美比赛过程中出现的大部分设备和服装都是由实际参赛者的家长提供。]]
编写剧本前，阿恩特在一次读报时看到有关[[阿诺德·施瓦辛格|阿诺德·施瓦辛格]]向一群高中生演讲的新闻，施瓦辛格说：“如果这世界上要有一件事我感到憎恨的话，那就是失败者。我鄙视他们。”为此阿恩特在剧本中讽刺了这种思想：“我觉得这种态度非常不好……我希望能够……抨击这种思想。人生在世总有成败得失……所以从一定程度上来说，儿童选美比赛是人们投入那些豪无意义竞争的缩影”<ref name="ForaInterview" />。导演乔纳森·戴顿也这样评价片中选美比赛的重要性：“无论选美比赛如何发展，对于我们来说，这都不是一部有关选美的电影，这点非常重要。这是一部有关失败者的作品，有关于你不知道自己最终将何去何从”<ref name="EpochTimesInterview" />。除阿比盖尔·布蕾斯琳外，片中所有参加选美比赛的女孩都是现实生活中的选美老将。她们的装扮和表演项目都与各自在实际参赛时相同<ref name="eFilmCritic">{{cite news | title = Interview with "Little Miss Sunshine" Directors Valerie Faris & Jonathan Dayton | last = Voynar | first = Kim | publisher = [http://efilmcritic.com/ eFilmCritic] | date = 2006-07-26 | url = http://www.efilmcritic.com/feature.php?feature=1897 | accessdate = 2013-07-31 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130731042216/http://www.efilmcritic.com/feature.php?feature=1897 | archivedate = 2013-07-31}}</ref>。导演在为影片拍摄做准备期间出席了南加州举办的多场选美赛事，还与一位协调员会过面，了解更多有关选美工作程序的事宜<ref name="TodayLN">{{cite news | title = Little Miss Vista | last = Smiley | first = Joanna | publisher = Today's Local News | date = 2006-09-07 | url = http://www.todayslocalnews.com/?sect=lifestyles&p=1704 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090109230236/http://www.todayslocalnews.com/?sect=lifestyles&p=1704 | archivedate = 2009-01-09 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2009-01-09}}</ref>。片中一位参赛选手的母亲声称，影片夸大了比赛过程中的一些内容：“大部分选美并不会像那样，把女孩腿上的毛递掉、在身上喷出类似于晒黑的颜色并且化上过分的浓妆”<ref name="TodayLN" />。

焦点影业起初希望电影在加拿大拍摄，但两位导演表示反对，认为让所有参加选美的女孩及其家长乘飞机前往该国的费用太高<ref name="NYTSmallFilm" />。于是众女孩和家人就在[[文图拉_(加利福尼亚州)|文图拉]]的一家酒店拍摄了两个星期，大部分设备和服务都是由孩子们的家长提供<ref name="TodayLN" /><ref name="DVDCommPageant">{{cite video | title = Little Miss Sunshine-(Commentary by Jonathan Dayton, Valerie Faris, and Michael Arndt) | medium = DVD | publisher = 20th Century Fox | time = 1:17:00 | date = 2006-12-19}}</ref>。为了让布蕾斯琳的角色在片中看起来比别的女孩“丰满”，她必须在拍摄时穿上填充式的服装<ref name="PeopleIntBreslin">{{cite news | title = Abigail Breslin..Is Little Miss A-List | last = Ellenson | first = Ruth Andrew | work = [[人物_(杂志)|People]] | date = 2006-08-07 | format = Registration required
| url = http://web.ebscohost.com.libproxy.sdsu.edu/ehost/detail?vid=1&hid=22&sid=2ff648e3-8661-4bdf-886d-7fc8992a54a4%40sessionmgr9 | accessdate = 2014-07-22}}</ref>。为了演好奥莉弗在片尾的舞蹈段落，布蕾斯琳还与一位[[编舞|编舞师]]一起练习了两个礼拜<ref name="MovieWebint" />。

== 发行 ==
=== 圣丹斯电影节 ===
[[File:Sundance-Film-Festival.jpg|upright]]举办的圣丹斯电影节上首次亮相]]
2006年1月20日，《阳光小美女》在2006年度圣丹斯电影节首映，多家电影公司参加了电影发行版权的投标，福克斯探照灯影业以1050万美元外加票房毛收入10%提成的条件中标<ref name="NYTSmallFilm" />。交易达成时影片首映还不到24小时，成交金额在该电影节历史上属最高之列<ref name="NYTDealHistory">{{cite news | title = Sundance Shines Light on Changes in Market | last = Halbfinger | first = David | work = The New York Times | date = 2006-01-28 | deadurl = no | publisher = The New York Times Company | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2006/01/28/movies/MoviesFeatures/28sund.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140722090427/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/01/28/movies/MoviesFeatures/28sund.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 | archivedate = 2014-07-22 | accessdate = 2014-07-22}}</ref><ref name="FilmFestival">{{cite news | title = First Major Acquisitions Deal Announced | last = Mandelberger | first = Sandy | publisher = [http://www.filmfestivalstv.com/ FilmFestivals.com] | date = 2006-01-22 | url = http://www.filmfestivalstv.com/sundance/2006/01/first_major_acq.html#more | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131022101542/http://www.filmfestivalstv.com/sundance/2006/01/first_major_acq.html#more | archivedate = 2013年10月22日 | df =  }}</ref>。之前的圣丹斯电影节上，《{{le|川流熙攘|Hustle & Flow}}》（{{lang|en|''Hustle & Flow''}}，[[2005年电影|2005年]]）以900万美元价格由[[派拉蒙优势影业|派拉蒙经典影业]]购得发行权，另外[[1999年电影|1999年]]的《{{le|快乐德州|Happy, Texas (film)}}》（{{lang|en|''Happy, Texas''}}）则以1000万美元的价格获[[米拉麦克斯影业|米拉麦克斯影业]]收购<ref name="FilmFestival" /><ref name="FilmFestival2">{{cite news | title = Picking up hot numbers in Park City | last = Chatelin | first = Bruno | publisher = [http://www.filmfestivalstv.com/ FilmFestivals.com] | date = 2006-02-02 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | url = http://www.filmfestivalstv.com/sundance/2006/02/picking_up_hot_.html#more | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131022101423/http://www.filmfestivalstv.com/sundance/2006/02/picking_up_hot_.html#more | archivedate = 2013年10月22日 | df =  }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
《阳光小美女》上映第一周只在美国的7家电影院发行，收入为49万8796美元<ref name="RTBoxOffice">{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/little_miss_sunshine/numbers.php | title = Little Miss Sunshine Box Office Summary | work = Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate = 2008-12-08 | deadurl = yes | publisher = Flixster | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081208153825/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/little_miss_sunshine/numbers.php | archivedate = 2008-12-08}}</ref>。2006年7月29日是电影开始初步限量放映后的第一个周六，影片在平均每家电影院进账2万零335美元<ref name="BOMPerTheater2">{{cite web | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-05-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130515143844/http://boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-07-28&p=.htm | publisher = IMDb | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-07-28&p=.htm | title = Daily Box Office (July 28-30) | work = Box Office Mojo }}</ref>。电影发行的前21天里，每天的单家电影院平均收入都是全美最高的，一直到8月15日才被{{lang|en|[[IMAX|IMAX]]}}影片《深海猎奇》（{{lang|en|''Deep Sea 3D''}}）超越<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-07-26&p=.htm | title = Daily Box Office (July 24-27) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023122442/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-07-26&p=.htm | deadurl = no | work = Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archivedate = 2012-10-23}}</ref><ref name="BOMPerTheater2" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-07-31&p=.htm | title = Daily Box Office (July 31-August 3) | work = Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023122449/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-07-31&p=.htm}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-08-04&p=.htm | title = Daily Box Office (August 4-6) | work = Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archivedate = 2014-07-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140708125611/http://boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-08-04&p=.htm | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-08-07&p=.htm | title = Daily Box Office (August 7-10) | work = Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140709183403/http://boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-08-07&p=.htm | archivedate = 2014-07-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Daily Box Office (August 11-13) | work = Box Office Mojo | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-08-11&p=.htm | publisher = IMDb | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140404210559/http://boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-08-11&p=.htm | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archivedate = 2014-04-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | work = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023122644/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-08-14&p=.htm | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/daily/chart/?sortdate=2006-08-14&p=.htm | title = Daily Box Office (August 14-17) | publisher = IMDb | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | accessdate = 2014-07-22}}</ref>。上映第三周时，《阳光小美女》进入了该周美国电影票房榜十强，并保持到发行后第11个星期才跌到了第11位<ref name="RTBoxOffice" />，最高时在第5周达到[[季军|季军]]位置，影片上映的电影院数量最高达到1602家<ref name="RTBoxOffice" />。国际方面，本片在[[法国|法国]]收入近850万美元，澳大利亚520万美元，[[德国|德国]]330万美元，[[西班牙|西班牙]]420万美元，[[意大利|意大利]]200万美元，[[英国|英国]]、[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]和[[马耳他|马耳他]]共计640万美元<ref name="BOMForeign">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-11-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131110000728/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=littlemisssunshine.htm | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=littlemisssunshine.htm | title = Little Miss Sunshine-Foreign Box Office | work = Box Office Mojo | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。影片在美国的总票房为5989万1098美元，其他国家4063万2083美元，共计1亿零52万3181美元<ref name="boxofficemojo" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
《阳光小美女》获得了广泛好评。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的208篇评论文章，其中有189篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”达91%，[[加权平均数|平均得分]]7.7（最高10分）<ref name="RTfresh">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601182051/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/little_miss_sunshine/ | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/little_miss_sunshine/ | title = Little Miss Sunshine (2006) | publisher = Flixster | work = Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate = 2014-07-22}}</ref>。而{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}上收集的36篇评论文章则有34篇给出好评，无差评，两篇褒贬不一，综合得分80（最高100）<ref name="MetaCritic">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130513153645/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/little-miss-sunshine | deadurl = no | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/little-miss-sunshine | title = Little Miss Sunshine | publisher = CBS | work = MetaCritic | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archivedate = 2013-05-13}}</ref>。

{{le|迈克尔·米德维|Michael Medved}}（{{lang|en|Michael Medved}}）给予影片四星（最高四星）的高度评价，称“……这部惊人而又不可抗拒的[[黑色幽默|黑色喜剧]]堪称今年最优秀的电影之一”，他还认为电影本身、导演乔纳森·戴顿和维莱莉·法瑞斯，以及演员艾伦·阿金、阿比盖尔·布蕾斯琳与史蒂夫·卡瑞尔都应该得到[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡奖]]提名<ref name="MichMed">{{cite news | title = Little Miss Sunshine | last = Medved | first = Michael | publisher = [http://www.medvedmovieminute.com/ MedvedMovieMinute] | accessdate = 2008-12-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.michaelmedved.com/pg/jsp/eot/review.jsp?pid=3049 | archivedate = 2008-12-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081208114951/http://www.michaelmedved.com/pg/jsp/eot/review.jsp?pid=3049}}</ref>。{{le|乔尔·西格尔|Joel Siegel}}（{{lang|en|Joel Siegel}}）也给出了罕见的“{{lang|en|A}}”级评分，称“除非[[奥森·威尔斯|奥森·威尔斯]]复生才有可能让这部电影无法登上我的年终十佳影片榜单”<ref name="ABCForecast">{{cite news | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | url = http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/JoelSiegel/story?id=2245032 | title = Forecast for 'Little Miss Sunshine': Oscar Heat | last = Siegel | first = Joel | publisher = ABC News | date = 2006-07-27 | archivedate = 2014-04-26 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140426020021/http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/JoelSiegel/story?id=2245032}}</ref>。[[BBC新闻|BBC新闻]]的斯特拉·帕帕迈克尔（{{lang|en|Stella Papamichael}}）称本片“以复杂性和愚蠢行径融合来取胜”<ref name="BBCReview">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2006/08/02/little_miss_sunshine_2006_review.shtml | title = Little Miss Sunshine (2006) | last = Papamichael | first = Stella | publisher = BBC News | date = 2006-09-05 | archivedate = 2012-11-13 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121113205430/http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2006/08/02/little_miss_sunshine_2006_review.shtml}}</ref>。克劳迪娅·普格（{{lang|en|Claudia Puig}}）在《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》撰文称赞了阿比盖尔·布蕾斯琳对奥莉弗一角的诠释：“如果由其他任何一个女孩来饰演奥莉弗，她都无法像片中（布蕾斯琳所做的）这样打动我们”<ref name="USAToday1">{{cite news | title = These kids are golden | last = Puig | first = Claudia | work = USA Today | date = 2006-12-21 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/printedition/life/20061222/wk_oscarkids22.art.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023171546/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/printedition/life/20061222/wk_oscarkids22.art.htm | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | accessdate = 2012-10-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的欧文·格雷伯曼（{{lang|en|Owen Gleiberman}}）对电影看法一般，评分只有“{{lang|en|C}}”，称其中的角色只是按照编剧的要求单调地走来走去讲出台词<ref name="EWReview">{{cite news|title=Movie Review: Little Miss Sunshine (2006) |last=Gleiberman |first=Owen |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2006-07-26 |accessdate=2014-07-22 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1219240,00.html |archivedate=2013-05-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512203009/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C1219240%2C00.html }}</ref>。《{{le|乡村之声|The Village Voice}}》（{{lang|en|''The Village Voice''}}）的吉姆·雷德利（{{lang|en|Jim Ridley}}）称这部电影就像是一辆“东倒西歪的汽车在走下坡路”，虽是从圣丹斯来的，但已“年久失修”<ref name="VillVoice">{{cite news|title=Ain't No Sunshine |last=Ridley |first=Jim |work=The Village Voice |date=2006-07-25 |accessdate=2014-07-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103221110/http://www.villagevoice.com/2006-07-18/film/ain-t-no-sunshine/ |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-11-03 |url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2006-07-18/film/ain-t-no-sunshine/ }}</ref>。《[[环球邮报|环球邮报]]》的利亚姆·莱西批评影片的人物塑造矫揉造作，角色的可爱和痛苦都有着明显的人工雕琢痕迹，电影的最终结论可谓既令人发指又让人振奋，似乎这样前面的那些炒作就都变得值得了<ref name="GlobeMailReview">{{cite news |title=Proust, Nietzsche and JonBenet |last=Lacey |first=Liam |work=Globe and Mail |date=2006-04-08 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/incoming/little-miss-sunshine-proust-nietzsche-and-jonbenet/article1101662/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vWdUR7Fn?url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/archives/little-miss-sunshine-proust-nietzsche-and-jonbenet/article838520/ |archivedate=2011-01-06 |accessdate=2014-07-22 }}</ref>。《[[国家评论|国家评论]]》的安娜·尼莫斯（{{lang|en|Anna Nimouse}}）声称，对于那些喜欢自己给自己添堵的影迷来说，这或许会是部“自我感觉良好”的电影。“如果你很悲惨，那么《阳光小美女》就是适合你的电影”<ref name="NationalReview">{{cite news | title = Little Miss Miserable | last = Nimouse | first = Anna | work = National Review | date = 2007-02-26 | url = http://www.nationalreview.com/articles/220092/little-miss-miserable/anna-nimouse | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140722105030/http://www.nationalreview.com/articles/220092/little-miss-miserable/anna-nimouse | archivedate = 2014-07-22 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《{{le|Paste (杂志)|Paste (magazine)|Paste}}》杂志将本片评为2000至2009十年间50部最佳电影的第34位<ref>{{cite web | title = The 50 Best Movies of the Decade (2000-2009) | url = http://www.pastemagazine.com/blogs/lists/2009/11/50-best-movies-of-the-decade-2000-2009.html?p=2 | work = Paste Magazine | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | date = 2009-11-03 | archivedate = 2013-12-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131229100617/http://www.pastemagazine.com/blogs/lists/2009/11/50-best-movies-of-the-decade-2000-2009.html?p=2}}</ref>。

{{lang|en|RogerEbert.com}}网站主编吉姆·爱默生（{{lang|en|Jim Emerson}}）这样描述电影的主题，称“《阳光小美女》向我们展现了一个世界，其中有表单、有宣传册、有过程、有职称、有节食食谱、有逐步定制的方案、有职业之路、有奖品，还有退休社区，这一切把所有人类的情感和欲望量化、排序并分类。所有这些内容都是可以分割的，也都可以转变成有关“赢家和输家”、用来自我提升的口头禅”<ref name="EmersonEbert">{{cite news | title = Little Miss Sunshine | last = Emerson | first = Jim | publisher = [http://www.rogerebert.com/ RogerEbert.com] | date = 2006-08-04 | url = http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/little-miss-sunshine-2006 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140104113126/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/little-miss-sunshine-2006 | archivedate = 2014-01-04}}</ref>。{{lang|en|UGO.com}}网站的布莱恩·托勒里科（{{lang|en|Brian Tallerico}}）也关注于本片的主题：《阳光小美女》告诉我们要坦然接受中间地带，认识到人生或许就像一场选美比赛，在那里经常会有人比我们更美、更聪明或者仅仅是运气更好，但只要我们走上台做回自己，一切都会好的<ref name="TallericoThemes">{{cite news | title = Little Miss Sunshine (Fox Searchlight) | last = Tallerico | first = Brian | publisher = UGO.com | url = http://www.ugo.com/channels/filmTv/features/littlemisssunshine/ | accessdate = 2011-06-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110615201210/http://www.ugo.com/channels/filmTv/features/littlemisssunshine/ | archivedate = 2011-06-15}}</ref>。

=== 家用媒体 ===
本片的{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}于2006年12月19日发行，其中包含双碟宽屏和全屏两种格式、两条评论音轨、四个不同结局以及{{lang|en|DeVotchKa}}乐队制作的一段[[音乐影片|音乐影片]]。{{lang|en|DVD}}发行首周销量排到第6位，销售额达到1961万4299美元<ref name="DVDSales">{{cite web | url = http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2006/LMSUN_dvd.php | title = Little Miss Sunshine — Weekly DVD Sales | publisher = The Numbers | accessdate = 2011-06-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611122654/http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2006/LMSUN_dvd.php | archivedate = 2011-06-11 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。到了2008年9月16日，{{lang|en|DVD}}在全美的总销售额已经达到5551万6832美元<ref name="DVDSales" />。截至2007年4月15日，{{lang|en|DVD}}的出租收入也达到了4632万美元<ref name="DVDRentals">{{cite web | url = http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=homevideo&id=littlemisssunshine.htm | title = Little Miss Sunshine DVD/Home Video | publisher = IMDb | work = Box Office Mojo | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131215113300/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=homevideo&id=littlemisssunshine.htm | archivedate = 2013-12-15 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。2009年2月10日，电影发行了[[蓝光光盘|蓝光影碟]]<ref name="Bluray">{{cite news | last = Salas | first = Randy A. | title = Classic films line up for Blu-ray | archivedate = 2014-07-22 | url = http://www.startribune.com/entertainment/tv/36895444.html?page=all&prepage=2&c=y#continue | work = Star Tribune | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140722111900/http://www.startribune.com/entertainment/tv/36895444.html?page=all&prepage=2&c=y}}</ref>。

