e news | title = ''Little Miss Sunshine'' improves Oscar prospects with win at Screen Actors Guild awards | agency = Associated Press | work = International Herald Tribune | date = 2007-01-29 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/01/29/arts/29iht-web.0130sagsun.4384317.html?_r=0 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140722114851/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/01/29/arts/29iht-web.0130sagsun.4384317.html?_r=0 | archivedate = 2014-07-22 | publisher = The New York Times Company}}</ref>和[[第5届华盛顿影评人协会奖|华盛顿影评人协会]]都授予本片最佳电影群体演出奖<ref name="NYTAwardsList">{{cite news | title = Little Miss Sunshine (2006) Awards | work = The New York Times | url = http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/335018/Little-Miss-Sunshine/awards | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121009065606/http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/335018/Little-Miss-Sunshine/awards | archivedate = 2012-10-09 | publisher = The New York Times Company}}</ref>。布蕾斯琳也获得了广播影评人协会<ref name="FOXAwards" />、[[爱荷华影评人协会|爱荷华影评人协会]]<ref name="NYTAwardsList" />、[[在线影评人协会|在线影评人协会]]<ref name="NYTAwardsList" />、[[凤凰城影评人协会|凤凰城影评人协会]]<ref name="FOXAwards" />和[[东京国际电影节|东京国际电影节]]的女演员奖项肯定<ref name="TokyoWin">{{cite news | title = Tokyo's top prize for "Spies" | last = Schilling | first = Mark | publisher = Variety | date = 2006-10-31 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070813172746/http://www.varietyasiaonline.com/content/view/263/53/ | archivedate = 2007-08-13 | url = http://www.varietyasiaonline.com/content/view/263/53/ | accessdate = 2007-08-13}}</ref>。

