=== 奥斯卡金像奖制片人争议 ===
由[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]颁发的奥斯卡最佳影片奖通常会授予获奖电影的[[电影监制|制片人]]，但对最终能够拿到小金人的制片人数量却存在一些争议。1999年，学院定出新规，最多可以有3位制片人因同一部电影获最佳影片奖<ref name="VarietyQuotes">{{cite news | title = Credits flap darkens ''Sunshine'' | last = Laporte | first = Nicole | author2 = McClintock, Pamela | work = Variety | date = 2007-02-17 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/2007/film/news/credits-flap-darkens-sunshine-1117959714/ | archivedate = 2014-07-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140722123329/http://variety.com/2007/film/news/credits-flap-darkens-sunshine-1117959714/}}</ref>。这一规则旨在防止一部影片获奖时出现大批相关制作人一起上台领奖的情况<ref name="NYTRelax">{{cite news | title = Oscar Rules Regarding Producing Are Relaxed | last = Cieply | first = Michael | work = The New York Times | date = 2007-06-14 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/14/movies/14acad.html?_r=2&ref=movies&oref=slogin& | publisher = The New York Times Company | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140722123617/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/14/movies/14acad.html?_r=2&ref=movies&oref=slogin& | archivedate = 2014-07-22 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[美国制片人协会|美国制片人协会]]没有对能因同一部电影获得表彰的制片人数量设限<ref name="LATRiles">{{cite news | title = Academy rule riles producers | last = Goldstein | first = Patrick | work = Los Angeles Times | archivedate = 2014-07-16 | date = 2007-02-27 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.latimes.com/env-et-gold20feb20-story.html | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140716114411/http://www.latimes.com/env-et-gold20feb20-story.html}}</ref>。《阳光小美女》共有5位制片人，分别是马克·图特尔陶布、大卫·弗兰德里、皮特·萨拉夫、阿尔伯特·伯格和罗恩·耶克萨，学院打算只让前三位上台领奖。伯格和耶克萨主要负责寻找剧本、挑选摄影师、协助结局的重新摄制并帮助影片参加圣丹斯电影节<ref name="EpochTimesInterview" /><ref name="LATimesProducers" /><ref name="HRRule">{{cite news | title = Oscars' rule of 3 cuts Grey, Berger, Yerxa | last = Kilday | first = Gregg | work = The Hollywood Reporter | date = 2007-01-27 | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-rule-3-cuts-grey-128901 | archivedate = 2014-07-22 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140722124902/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-rule-3-cuts-grey-128901}}</ref>。学院同意，这两位也是电影制作过程中的合伙人，但宣称只有部分制片人能够得到学院认可。该机构认为伯格和耶克萨的工作是集体努力的组成部分，但拒绝让两人也获得奖项<ref name="VarietyQuotes" />。制片人{{le|大卫·郝伯曼|David Hoberman}}（{{lang|en|David Hoberman}}）对此表示，他支持5位制片人都获奖，“如果确实有5人参与了电影的制作，那就没有理由非要排除哪位制片人获奖的可能”<ref name="VarietyQuotes" />。{{le|琳达·奥布斯特|Lynda Obst}}（{{lang|en|Lynda Obst}}）是奥斯卡金像奖制片人委员会成员，她对此表示：“总的来说，一部电影并不是靠5个人拍成的。如果这次是个意外的话，那的确很遗憾，但是，我们不应该为了一个意外而取消规则”<ref name="VarietyQuotes" />。

在第79届奥斯卡颁奖典礼上，制片人马克·图特尔陶布、大卫·弗兰德里和皮特·萨拉夫一起上台领取了原著剧本奖，而美国制片人协会之前已经表彰了全部5位制片人<ref name="VarietyOver">{{cite news | title = Academy bends on "rule of three" | last = McNary | first = Dave | work = Variety | date = 2007-12-14 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/1993/film/news/vr-s-first-stop-won-t-be-at-home-104697/ | archivedate = 2014-07-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140720135328/http://variety.com/1993/film/news/vr-s-first-stop-won-t-be-at-home-104697/}}</ref>。阿尔伯特·伯格对于学院的决定表示：“管他学院怎么说，这电影都是我们制作的”<ref name="LATimesProducers" />。2007年6月，学院宣布将来会允许一部电影有超过3位制片人领奖，称“委员会有权决定在极少的例外情况下允许多位符合资格的制片人获得提名”<ref name="VarietyOver" />。

