=== 电影配乐 ===
《阳光小美女》的[[电影配乐|电影配乐]]由[[丹佛|丹佛]]乐队{{le|DeVotchKa}}和作曲家[[麦切尔·丹纳|麦切尔·丹纳]]共同谱写<ref name="MovieWebProd" />，{{lang|en|DeVotchKa}}演奏，大部分音乐都是根据已有歌曲改编，如《{{lang|en|How It Ends}}》就改编成了《{{lang|en|The Winner Is}}》，还采用了专辑《{{lang|en|How It Ends}}》中的歌曲《{{lang|en|The Enemy Guns}}》和《{{lang|en|You Love Me}}》，以及专辑《{{lang|en|Una Volta}}》中的《{{lang|en|La Llorona}}》。

戴顿和法瑞斯通过[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]的{{le|KCRW}}广播电台听到了歌曲《{{lang|en|You Love Me}}》，由此开始接触{{lang|en|DeVotchKa}}的音乐<ref name="CSMDeVotch">{{cite news | title = DeVotchKa's music is as offbeat as its name | last = Sullivan | first = Jim | work = The Christian Science Monitor | date = 2006-07-28 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | url = http://www.csmonitor.com/2006/0728/p13s01-almp.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121012070145/http://www.csmonitor.com/2006/0728/p13s01-almp.html | archivedate = 2012-10-12}}</ref>。两位导演对这些音乐留下了非常深刻的印象，以致于还为众演员购买了包含{{lang|en|DeVotchKa}}专辑音乐的[[IPod|IPod]]<ref name="RollStone">{{cite news | title = Devotchka: The Best Little Grammy-Nominated Band You’ve Never Heard Of | last = Hoard | first = Christian | work = Rolling Stone | date = 2007-02-07 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/devotchka-the-best-little-grammy-nominated-band-youve-never-heard-of-20070207 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archivedate = 2013-02-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130203104413/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/devotchka-the-best-little-grammy-nominated-band-youve-never-heard-of-20070207}}</ref>。麦切尔·丹纳的加入主要是帮助编排已有素材，并同{{lang|en|DeVotchKa}}在为影片创作的新素材上合作。由于电影配乐中有太高的比例改编自{{lang|en|DeVotchKa}}的已有作品，因此《阳光小美女》没有资格参加[[奥斯卡最佳原创配乐奖|奥斯卡最佳原创配乐奖]]的角逐<ref name="78AARules">{{cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/78academyawards/rules/index_text.html |title=78th Academy Awards Rules |publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |accessdate=2008-12-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208133937/http://www.oscars.org/78academyawards/rules/index_text.html |archivedate=2008-12-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{lang|en|DeVotchKa}}的歌曲《{{lang|en|Til the End of Time}}》获得了卫星奖的最佳原创歌曲奖提名<ref name="InPreAcad">{{cite news | title = The 11th Annual Satellite Awards Nominees | publisher = International Press Academy | url = http://www.pressacademy.com/satawards/ipa-sa-nominees.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111111091639/http://www.pressacademy.com/satawards/ipa-sa-nominees.html | archivedate = 2011-11-11 | accessdate = 2011-11-11}}</ref>，并且{{lang|en|DeVotchKa}}和丹纳都因本片的音乐而获得了[[第49届格莱美奖|2007年格莱美奖]]提名<ref name="RollStone" />。

