《阳光小美女》的[[原声音乐|电影原声带]]最高在2006年的美国“热门独立唱片榜”上排到第42位，还在“热带电影原声带榜”上排到第24位<ref name="AllBill">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-11-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131124060627/http://www.allmusic.com/album/little-miss-sunshine-original-soundtrack-mw0000438864 | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/little-miss-sunshine-original-soundtrack-mw0000438864 | title = Little Miss Sunshine Original Soundtrack Billboard | publisher = Allmusic | accessdate = 2014-07-22}}</ref>。其中包括有{{le|塞扬·史蒂文斯|Sufjan Stevens}}（{{lang|en|Sufjan Stevens}}）的两首歌曲（分别是《{{lang|en|No Man's Land}}》和《{{lang|en|Chicago}}》），以及托尼·提斯代尔（{{lang|en|Tony Tisdale}}）的《{{lang|en|Catwalkin'}}》和里克·詹姆斯的《{{lang|en|Super Freak}}》<ref name="MovieWebProd" /><ref name="AllBill" />。此外，片中还有两首由{{le|戈登·普古达|Gordon Pogoda}}创作的歌曲，分别是《{{lang|en|Let It Go}}》和《{{lang|en|You've Got Me Dancing}}》，其中后一首歌是由普古达和巴里·厄普顿（{{lang|en|Barry Upton}}）共同谱写，这两首歌都出现在片尾的选美戏段中<ref name="YahooMovie">{{cite web | url = http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/1809257696/cast | title = Little Miss Sunshine (2006) | work = Yahoo! Movies | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120111015442/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/1809257696/cast | archivedate = 2012-01-11 | accessdate = 2012-01-11 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。奥莉弗在选美比赛才艺表演环节跳舞时采用的背景音乐《{{lang|en|Super Freak}}》是于电影[[后期制作|后期制作]]期间在音乐总监的建议下加入的<ref name="DVDCommMusic">{{cite video | title = Little Miss Sunshine-(Commentary by Jonathan Dayton, Valerie Faris, and Michael Arndt) | medium = DVD | publisher = 20th Century Fox | time = 1:31:48 | date = 2006-12-19}}</ref>。阿恩特的剧本中提及了[[王子_(音乐家)|王子]]的歌曲《{{lang|en|Peach}}》，不过到实际拍摄时采用的是{{lang|en|[[ZZ_Top|ZZ Top]]}}的歌曲《{{lang|en|Gimme All Your Lovin'}}》<ref name="DVDCommMusic" />。

