== 2011年音乐舞台剧 ==
{{main|{{le|小太陽的願望 (音樂劇)|Little Miss Sunshine (musical)}}}}
2009年10月25日至11月7日，佛罗里达州{{le|尤利 (佛罗里达州)|Yulee, Florida|尤利}}（{{lang|en|Yulee}}）的{{le|圣丹斯协会|Sundance Institute}}白橡木实验剧院排演了一部根据本片改编的[[音乐剧|音乐剧]]，词曲由{{le|威廉·芬恩|William Finn}}（{{lang|en|William Finn}}）创作，{{le|詹姆斯·拉皮尼|James Lapine}}（{{lang|en|James Lapine}}）导演<ref>{{cite web|date=2009-09-22 |accessdate=2014-07-22 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.sundance.org/pdf/2009-09-22-TheatreLabWhiteOak2009_FINAL.pdf |title=TWO ORIGINAL MUSICALS LIKE WATER FOR CHOCOLATE AND LITTLE MISS SUNSHINE,  SELECTED FOR ANNUAL SUNDANCE INSTITUTE THEATRE LAB AT WHITE OAK OCTOBER 25 - NOVEMBER 8, 2009 |publisher=Sundance Institute |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207045500/http://www.sundance.org/pdf/2009-09-22-TheatreLabWhiteOak2009_FINAL.pdf |archivedate=2013-12-07|format=[[PDF|PDF]] }}</ref>。然后节目于2011年2月15日在{{le|拉霍亚剧场|La Jolla Playhouse}}[[首演|首演]]，一直上演到同年3月27日<ref name="stageshow">{{cite web | title = Little Miss Sunshine | publisher = La Jolla Playhouse | url = http://www.lajollaplayhouse.org/the-season/plays/little-miss-sunshine | archivedate = 2011-04-01 | accessdate = 2011-04-01 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110401172350/http://www.lajollaplayhouse.org/the-season/plays/little-miss-sunshine}}</ref>。主要演员包括亨特·福斯特（{{lang|en|Hunter Foster}}）、马尔科姆·格茨（{{lang|en|Malcolm Gets}}）、格奥尔基·詹姆斯（{{lang|en|Georgi James}}）、迪克·莱特沙（{{lang|en|Dick Latessa}}）、{{le|詹妮弗·劳拉·汤普森|Jennifer Laura Thompson}}（{{lang|en|Jennifer Laura Thompson}}）和{{le|泰勒·特林奇|Taylor Trensch}}（{{lang|en|Taylor Trensch}}）<ref>{{cite news | last = Hebert | first = James | date = 2010-12-17 | title = The "Sunshine" set: Playhouse announces new musical's cast | url = http://www.utsandiego.com/news/2010/dec/17/the-sunshine-set-playhouse-announces-musicals/ | work = San Diego Union Tribune | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121018034244/http://www.utsandiego.com/news/2010/dec/17/the-sunshine-set-playhouse-announces-musicals/ | archivedate = 2012-10-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Jones |first=Kenneth |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105133712/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/147650-Road-Trip-Finn-Lapines-Little-Miss-Sunshine-Musical-Begins-World-Premiere-Run-in-CA |work=playbill.com |archivedate=2013-11-05 |url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/147650-Road-Trip-Finn-Lapines-Little-Miss-Sunshine-Musical-Begins-World-Premiere-Run-in-CA |title=Road Trip! Finn & Lapine's 'Little Miss Sunshine' Musical Begins World-Premiere Run in CA |accessdate=2014-07-22 }}</ref>。2011年3月11日，马尔科姆·格茨离开了节目，他演出的弗兰克一角由安德鲁·萨蒙斯基接替，替补演员莱恩·瓦格纳则接手乔书亚·罗斯（{{lang|en|Joshua Rose}}）一角直至节目于2011年3月27日谢幕<ref name="stageshow" />。

